{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"ht_social_micro_T6jtkW":{"type":"ht-social-micro","blocks":{"chapter_RQmBUw":{"type":"chapter","settings":{"icon_svg":"","icon_color":"#1a1a1a","icon_size":72,"title":"","caption":"","story":"<p>At Hide Tallow, we stand behind the quality of every product we make — but because our products are natural, topical, and personal-use, there are specific limits around what can and can’t be returned. Please read this policy carefully before ordering.<\/p>","media_layout":"scroll","media_snap":true,"media_height":360,"media_gap":12,"media_radius":12,"media_bg":"#f7f7f7"}},"chapter_LB3NeR":{"type":"chapter","settings":{"icon_svg":"<svg viewbox=\"0 0 48 48\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" fill=\"#000000\"><g id=\"SVGRepo_bgCarrier\" stroke-width=\"0\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_tracerCarrier\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_iconCarrier\"> <path d=\"M0 0h48v48H0z\" fill=\"none\"><\/path> <g id=\"Shopicon\"> <path d=\"M10,22v2c0,7.72,6.28,14,14,14s14-6.28,14-14s-6.28-14-14-14h-6.662l3.474-4.298l-3.11-2.515L10.577,12l7.125,8.813 l3.11-2.515L17.338,14H24c5.514,0,10,4.486,10,10s-4.486,10-10,10s-10-4.486-10-10v-2H10z\"><\/path> <\/g> <\/g><\/svg>","icon_color":"#1a1a1a","icon_size":72,"title":"Returns & Exchanges","caption":"","story":"<p>We do not accept returns of opened or used products under any circumstance. We also cannot accept returns for scent preferences, texture preferences, skin feel, or general dissatisfaction. Since cosmetic products cannot be verified as “unopened” once received, returns for unused products are not supported either. <\/p><p>The only exception is when there is a clear issue with the product itself, such as receiving the wrong item or an abnormality that indicates a production error. In those cases, reach out within seven days of delivery and we will review and assist.<\/p>","media_layout":"scroll","med