ce of both the outer packaging and the product. Once provided, we will open an investigation with the carrier. Replacements are issued only after the carrier completes their review and confirms the claim.<\/p>","media_layout":"scroll","media_snap":true,"media_height":360,"media_gap":12,"media_radius":12,"media_bg":"#f7f7f7"}},"chapter_HekfMd":{"type":"chapter","settings":{"icon_svg":"<svg viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><g id=\"SVGRepo_bgCarrier\" stroke-width=\"0\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_tracerCarrier\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_iconCarrier\"> <path d=\"M7.28451 10.3333C7.10026 10.8546 7 11.4156 7 12C7 14.7614 9.23858 17 12 17C14.7614 17 17 14.7614 17 12C17 9.23858 14.7614 7 12 7C11.4156 7 10.8546 7.10026 10.3333 7.28451\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M12 2V4\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M12 20V22\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M4 12L2 12\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M22 12L20 12\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M19.7778 4.22266L17.5558 6.25424\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M4.22217 4.22266L6.44418 6.25424\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M6.44434 17.5557L4.22211 19.7779\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <path d=\"M19.7778 19.7773L17.5558 17.5551\" stroke=\"#ff9300\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><\/path> <\/g><\/svg>","icon_color":"#ffffff","icon_size":104,"title":"Melted Products","caption":"","story":"<p>Tallow is a natural fat and may melt in warm climates or during transit, especially in summer months. Melting is normal and does not affect product quality. Your product will resolidify at room temperature. Because this is expected behavior, melted products are not eligible for refunds or replacements.<\/p>","media_layout":"scroll","media_snap":true,"media_height":360,"media_gap":12,"media_radius":12,"media_bg":"#f7f7f7"}},"chapter_GFjLVM":{"type":"chapter","settings":{"icon_svg":"<svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" fill=\"#000000\" class=\"bi bi-question-square\"><g id=\"SVGRepo_bgCarrier\" stroke-width=\"0\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_tracerCarrier\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><\/g><g id=\"SVGRepo_iconCarrier\"> <path d=\"M14 1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h12zM2 0a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2z\"><\/path> <path d=\"M5.255 5.786a.237.237 0 0 0 .241.247h.825c.138 0 .248-.113.266-.25.09-.656.54-1.134 1.342-1.134.686 0 1.314.343 1.314 1.168 0 .635-.374.927-.965 1.371-.673.489-1.206 1.06-1.168 1.987l.003.217a.25.25 0 0 0 .25.246h.811a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-.105c0-.718.273-.927 1.01-1.486.609-.463 1.244-.977 1.244-2.056 0-1.511-1.276-2.241-2.673-2.241-1.267 0-2.655.59-2.75 2.286zm1.557 5.763c0 .533.425.927 1.01.927.609 0 1.028-.394 1.028-.927 0-.552-.42-.94-1.029-.94-.584 0-1.009.388-1.009.94z\"><\/path> <\/g><\/svg>","icon_color":"#0e3a27","icon_size":56,"title":"Lost or Stolen Packages","caption":"","story":"<p>If a package is marked as delivered but cannot be found, the customer must first contact the carrier and open a missing-package case. We will also open a support ticket on our side. After the carrier finishes their investigation, we can determine next steps based on the official findings. We cannot replace or refund orders marked as delivered unless the investigation supports it.<\/p>","media_layout":"scroll","media_snap":true,"media_height":360,"media_gap":12,"media_radius":12,"media_bg":"#f7f7f7"}},"chapter_LVPVWa":{"type":"chapter","settings":{"icon_svg":"<svg viewbox=\"0 0 4